          <Pad Id="CuYxC5vND05MJUSVILEnJe" Comment="" Bounds="1277,510,312,132" ShowValueBox="true" isIOBox="true" Value="[&#xD;&#xA;  &quot;\u003Cthink\u003E\nOkay, the user said \u0022hello\u0022. I need to respond politely. Let me make sure to greet them back and ask how I can assist. Keep it friendly and open-ended. Maybe add an emoji to keep the tone light. Let me check for any typos. Alright, that should do it.\n\u003C/think\u003E\n\nHello! How can I assist you today? \uD83D\uDE0A&quot;&#xD;&#xA;]" />
